	<div class="GameModeFAQ">		
		<h2> There are several types of game modes. </h2>
		
		<h3>By Match</h3>		
		<p>This game mode is for betting about the final score of a single match. Players can bet about: </p>
			<ul>
				<li> The exact minute of the first goal </li>
				<li> Which team gets the first goal </li>
				<li> How many red or yellow cards there will be </li>
				<li> Basically anything else you could predict about the match
			</ul>
		<h3>By Jornada</h3>
		<p>This game mode is for betting about the final score of each match in the jornada. Players can also bet about: </p>
			<ul>
				<li>Which team is going to win as home or as visitor</li>
				<li> In which match there will be a tie </li>
			</ul>
		<h3> By League</h3>
		<p> This game mode is about betting for the final champion of the league </p>			
			
